{"tid":102563,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［一人一人個］由小事、但令你改變生活習慣既經歷","createTime":"2017-01-31T17:12:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-02T09:01:05.000Z","uid":64800,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ecdce9804942bb87f3a3177a34894093aaaa7a1c","tid":102563,"uid":64800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T17:12:03.000Z","msg":"等我拋個磚引玉先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1. 我中學有個班主任有臭狐、個胳肋底長期濕勁嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自此我成日留意自己胳肋底既清潔，每日沖涼一定重點洗一洗佢。<br />\n<br />\n2. 有次去朋友屋企玩、咁岩撞正有人跳樓（死況慘烈）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自此每次準備入大廈前都習慣望一望上面，好怕比人澤死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aa1f54cd62d0c710ebe1f8e0532a987f6a95691","tid":102563,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T17:15:40.000Z","msg":"細個人地教我上 <a href=\"http://pk.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpk.com&d=MHEGAcVJLkfiWkVsZ9yRxhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=bb67864c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">pk.com</a><br />\n搞到依家成日要打丁"},{"pid":"9660ede805877f034906c4a8b5154dc10a950eb9","tid":102563,"uid":31384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T17:25:01.000Z","msg":"以前飲罐裝飲品，從來唔會抹乾淨個罐頂就飲<br />\n當見過一箱箱放地下原來有機會經歷唔同嘅恐怖慨洗禮<br />\n我盡量買樽裝，罐装一定抹得好乾淨先飲<br />\n便利店買罐紅牛抹一抹你就知<br />\n10罐有8罐汚"},{"pid":"16d5cc239d93bc75679e1e766860d1b7496cc25a","tid":102563,"uid":9681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T17:26:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細個人地教我上 <a href=\"http://pk.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpk.com&d=MHEGAcVJLkfiWkVsZ9yRxhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=bb67864c\" target=\"_blank\">http://pk.com</a><br />\n搞到依家成日要打丁</blockquote><br />\n仲有咩網站咁邪惡？<br />\n<br />\n等我ban哂佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdc91a88b806f59fdcab7a9cb35ca